---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import hero from "/public/about_hero.webp";
import Button from "../components/Button.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Pennine Digital - About">
  <section class="relative min-h-[70vh] mt-20 flex items-center bg-background">
    <img src={hero.src} alt="Moorland landscape in West Yorkshire" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover" />

    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-black/40 via-black/50 to-black/40"></div>

    <div class="relative max-w-2xl mx-auto px-6 text-background">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-heading font-semibold">About Pennine Digital</h1>

      <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-light/90 leading-relaxed">
        Pennine Digital is a small web studio based in West Yorkshire, creating clean, modern websites for local businesses — taking the
        stress out of getting online and building something that genuinely helps you grow.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-24 bg-background">
    <div class="px-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-heading mb-6">The person behind the work</h2>

      <p class="text-dark/80">
        I'm Chris — a front-end developer based in Riddlesden, West Yorkshire. I've spent the last few years honing modern development
        skills, building projects, and shaping a way of working that focuses on clarity, reliability, and thoughtful design.
      </p>

      <p class="mt-5 text-dark/80">
        Before moving into development, I spent several years working in hospitality. It taught me how to communicate clearly, stay
        organised, and look after people — skills that matter just as much when building websites as they do writing code.
      </p>

      <p class="mt-5 text-dark/80">
        Pennine Digital is where those experiences come together: modern development, considered design, and a friendly, straightforward
        approach to helping small businesses across West Yorkshire get online.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-28 bg-background/60">
    <div class="px-6 text-center max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-heading">What I care about</h2>

      <p class="mt-4 text-dark/70 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        The way a website is built matters just as much as how it looks. These are the principles that guide how I approach every project.
      </p>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-10 mt-12">
        <div class="bg-white border border-dark/10 rounded-lg p-7 hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-heading font-semibold">Clarity</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-dark/70 leading-relaxed">
            Everything is explained in plain language, without jargon or unnecessary complexity. You should always understand what’s
            happening and why.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border border-dark/10 rounded-lg p-7 hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-heading font-semibold">Reliability</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-dark/70 leading-relaxed">
            When I commit to something, I follow through. Clear communication, realistic timelines, and dependable support matter just as
            much as the website itself.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border border-dark/10 rounded-lg p-7 hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-heading font-semibold">Craftsmanship</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-dark/70 leading-relaxed">
            Good websites should feel calm, fast, and thoughtfully built. I focus on clean structure, performance, and details that make the
            experience better for your customers.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-background pt-28">
    <div class="px-6 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
      <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl md:text-4xl">Why I started Pennine Digital</h2>

      <p class="text-dark/80 mt-4">
        I noticed many local businesses were stuck between expensive agencies and DIY website builders that didn't quite hit the mark. There
        was a gap for something in the middle — a personal, reliable service that builds websites from scratch and delivers something that
        genuinely fits your business.
      </p>

      <p class="text-dark/80 mt-4">
        That's what I set out to create: a small, local studio with a straightforward, honest approach to helping you get online.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="text-center py-24">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-heading text-dark/80 mb-10">Ready to chat about your website? I’d love to hear from you.</h3>
      <Button href="/contact" title="Get in touch" variant="light" />
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
